snippet.title: Super Hind - The World's Deadliest Assault Copter
snippet.description:
Trailer of a PSP-exclusive helicopter action game Super Hind developed by Mountain Sheep.

High Quality version: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qMpsEjO3Q8Y&fmt=18

20TH CENTURY ASSAULT COPTER. 21ST CENTURY UPGRADE:
The Russian MI-45D Super Hind can out-maneuver and out-fight virtually anything on land, sea or air. You are pilot Warrant Officer Dante Griffin. In your hands is a weapon that can change the world.

http://www.superhind.com
http://www.mountainsheep.net
